<div class="container">
  <h2>Deliverables</h2>
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-6">
      <h3>User stories</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>
          As a commuter, I want the application to remember my most commonly used destination, so that I can find a route to work quickly.  
        </li>
        <li>As a student, I want to take the fastest route to class so that I can make it there on time.</li>
        <li>As a user, I want an easy to understand interface so that it's not hard to find and follow a route.</li>
        <li>As a user I want to see a visualization of the map so that I know where I am in relation to everywhere else.</li>
        <li>As a user I want to hear the spoken directions so that I can use the app hands-free.</li>
        <li>As a user I want to be able to see the traffic if possible so that I can get a better idea of traffic congestion.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>